{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Restructure Around the Visitor\n      Reorganize the page around three questions a visitor asks: \"Is this for me?\" → \"What are you actually doing?\" → \"What can I do?\" Each question gets a section. The framework (PolicyOS, foundations) becomes the answer to question 2 — the proof that there's a real plan, not just complaints.\n      Recommended. Puts the visitor at the center. Every section earns its place by answering a real question. More work to write, but the structure is honest about what a homepage is for.","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1777675091910}
